pageProduct.name: Swisse Skincare Manuka Honey Glow Boosting Moisturiser 120ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

With Vitamin C, Grape Seed Oil and Shea Butter

Swisse Manuka Honey Glow Boosting Moisturiser is a supercharged formula to help plump and hydrate the skin, for a more supple and radiant complexion. It features stabilised Vitamin C, Grape Seed Oil and Shea Butter for added goodness

Suitable For: Normal Skin

Size: 120mL

Warnings

Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner.

Ingredients

AQUA (Water)
Glycerin (Plant Derived)
GRAPE SEED Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil
Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter
Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride
Glyceryl Stearate SE
Cetearyl Alcohol
MANUKA HONEY Honey (Mel)
Fragrance (Natural fragrance)
Sodium Hyaluronate
Sodium Ascorbyl Phosphate
Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate
Xanthan Gum
Citric Acid
Sodium Citrate
Benzyl Alcohol
Dehydroacetic Acid

Directions

Apply as required to face and décolletage. Massage gently into skin in a circular motion.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store upright below 28°C.
